# GuildOS — 7D Framework

Python multi-service AI agent coordination app on Base Sepolia. 7-day hackathon build, scope locked.

## Read Before Coding

- `docs/TECH_STACK.md` — stack, component names, decision log
- `docs/MVP_FLOW.md` — 15-step loop; if not in these steps, it's out of scope
- `docs/RISKS.md` — fallbacks are decided; don't re-evaluate

## Component Registry

| Component | File |
|-----------|------|
| OrchestratorServer | `src/orchestrator/server.py` |
| OrchestratorTools | `src/orchestrator/tools.py` |
| SpecialistAgent | `src/specialist/agent.py` |
| A2AClient | `src/shared/a2a.py` |
| ERC8004 | `src/shared/erc8004.py` |
| AgentFightClub | `src/shared/agentfightclub.py` |
