## Rules

- Base Sepolia only — no mainnet
- No keys in source files — env vars only
- Human gates must halt and wait for `y/N`
- `giveFeedback()` caller: guild contract or Marco's EOA (NOT Specialist wallet — F2)
- Log all A2A messages to `./logs/a2a_trace_{date}.json`
- Log all GLM-5.1 traces to `./logs/glm_trace_{date}.json`

## Don't

- Add features not in the 15-step MVP flow
- Call the live ERC-8004 registry for talent matching (hardcoded profile)
- Build UI — terminal is the demo surface
- Implement ragequit on-chain (document only)
- Skip pytest or ruff before marking a task done
